snippet.title: THE STAND: Amber Heard Says New Series About Fictional Pandemic Raises Big Questions
snippet.description:
The upcoming pandemic epic "The Stand" is about a fictional virus far deadlier than COVID-19 and how the few people left on Earth have to pull together to survive.

Amber Heard, who's among the all-star cast of the CBS All Access show, says the story raises all sorts of questions.

"I believe an audience will think, 'What would I do? What would I be willing to give up? What would I be willing to try?'" says Heard, who plays a woman lured to the dark side of those who survive the fictional pandemic.

#AmberHeard #TheStand #CBS
